      "authorResponded": true,
      "body": "Does DINOv2(patch) model correspond to DINO-WM's best configuration model? If yes, then DINO-WM paper reports 28% for GD and 86% for CEM **open-loop planning** at A5.3 appendix section. Are there any differences in evaluation that I might be misunderstanding?",
