          "authorResponded": false,
          "body": "Thanks for your question! Yes, DINOv2(patch) is DINO-WM and the reported values are GD. We improve the GD open-loop planning for *all* models by using an Adam optimizer (which helps the most!) and more suitable hyperparameters (see Table 5 in page19).",
